headline: 5 Must-Read Analyst Questions From Western Digital’s Q1 Earnings Call
summary: Western Digital delivered a first quarter that outperformed market expectations, with management attributing the results to robust demand from hyperscale data center customers and a rapid ramp-up of its highest-capacity hard drives.
